messages.text:
Looks like adding this to my settings.json did the trick for Windows. For *nix, I think you might want to end with a ":" rather than ";" per the documentation.
```{
    ....
    "terminal.integrated.env.windows": {
        "JULIA_LOAD_PATH":"${workspaceFolder};"
    },
    ...
}```

